message reader
- scheduled, fixed delay of 60 seconds
- upon reading new incoming message, fire an event
- @TODO: enable random delay

local message writer
- scheduled, fixed delay of 60 seconds
- upon reading new incoming message, fire an event
- allows for manually queuing messages by placing files in the appropriate location
- @TODO: enable random delay

amazon / local message service
- listens for events
- on incoming event, persist in appropriate location

specific handler / event listener
- on incoming event (from message reader (amazon / local)) process event